{"ja336:0.1":"Jataka ","ja336:0.2":"Catukkanipata ","ja336:0.3":"Kokilavagga ","ja336:0.4":"6. Brahachattajataka ","ja336:1.1":"“Tinam tinanti lapasi, ","ja336:1.2":"ko nu te tinamahari; ","ja336:1.3":"Kim nu te tinakiccatthi, ","ja336:1.4":"tinameva pabhasasi”. ","ja336:2.1":"“Idhagama brahmacari, ","ja336:2.2":"braha chatto bahussuto; ","ja336:2.3":"So me sabbam samadaya, ","ja336:2.4":"tinam nikkhippa gacchati”. ","ja336:3.1":"“Evetam hoti kattabbam, ","ja336:3.2":"appena bahumicchata; ","ja336:3.3":"Sabbam sakassa adanam, ","ja336:3.4":"anadanam tinassa ca”. ","ja336:3.5":"(…) ","ja336:4.1":"“Silavanto na kubbanti, ","ja336:4.2":"balo silani kubbati; ","ja336:4.3":"Aniccasilam dussilyam, ","ja336:4.4":"kim pandiccam karissati”ti. ","ja336:5.1":"Brahachattajatakam chattham. "}